01:20:06,690 --> 01:20:08,927
I just couldn't believe it.

1126
01:20:19,523 --> 01:20:22,654
I think I just forgot about you, Lizzie.

1127
01:20:23,362 --> 01:20:24,889
You know?

1128
01:20:26,403 --> 01:20:28,835
You were just a child.

1129
01:20:28,835 --> 01:20:32,131
So little.

1130
01:20:36,003 --> 01:20:38,043
But you needed me.

1131
01:20:39,939 --> 01:20:44,228
And that forced me
to pay attention again.

1132
01:20:44,228 --> 01:20:45,919
You know what I mean?

1133
01:20:48,196 --> 01:20:50,529
I had to take care of you.

1134
01:20:52,899 --> 01:20:57,092
And in a way,
you brought me back to life...

1135
01:20:57,092 --> 01:21:00,158
...and you became everything
