01:21:09,668 --> 01:21:14,500
But God, you were so full
of promise, Lizzie.

1138
01:21:14,500 --> 01:21:19,170
And I wanted so much
for you in your life.

1139
01:21:20,932 --> 01:21:25,275
And I couldn't see
that it wasn't good for you.

1140
01:21:29,478 --> 01:21:31,386
You just...

1141
01:21:32,005 --> 01:21:34,307
